//Previous interventions / therapies - Radio

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Mamma MRI
When	I select 'No' radio button
Then 'Add new finding' button is disabled
When	I select 'Yes' radio button
Then 'Previous interventions / therapies' dropdown menu is enabled
When I select 'Radiotherapy' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Ongoing' radio button is enabled
And 'Date untill' radio button is enabled
And single selection Localizer is enabled
When I select 'Date untill' radio button
Then 'Month' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Year' dropdown menu is enabled
When	I select 'R' on the Localizer
Then 'R' part turns red
When I select 'L' on the Localizer
Then 'L' part turns red
And	'R' part is automatically deselected and turns white